ur d'itin&#233;raire tiennent compte des travaux.&nbsp;<br><br>Motif : travaux sur le r&#233;seau ferroviaire (SNCF R&#201;SEAU effectue une remise &#224; neuf compl&#232;te de 13,4 kilom&#232;tres de voie entre Mortcerf et Coulommiers afin d&#8217;am&#233;liorer le confort et la r&#233;gularit&#233; lors de vos d&#233;placements en train).<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic perturbé","impactedSections":[{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01730","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:67920","name":"Coulommiers (Coulommiers)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:71359","name":"Gare de l'Est (Paris)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01730","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:71359","name":"Gare de l'Est (Paris)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:67920","name":"Coulommiers (Coulommiers)"}}],"disruption_id":"7bf21e65-8121-431f-8e14-7d34eb67cf3e"},{"id":"83e9719e-e068-4cfc-a876-cc1bcc923c11","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260602T101937","end":"20260602T121900"}],"lastUpdate":"20260602T102250","cause":"PERTURBATION","severity":"PERTURBEE","title":"Ligne N : Mantes-la-Jolie <-> Plaisir - Grignon trafic ralenti","message":"<p>Le trafic est ralenti entre Mantes-la-Jolie et Plaisir - Grignon dans les 2 sens.<br><br>Pour plus d'informations sur cette perturbation, consultez le <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/lignesNetU_SNCF\">fil X de la ligne N<\/a>.<br><br>Motif : accident &#224; un passage &#224; niveau dans le secteur de Beynes<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic perturbé","impactedSections":[{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01736","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:64199","name":"Plaisir - Grignon (Plaisir)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:65931","name":"Mantes-la-Jolie (Mantes-la-Jolie)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01736","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:65931","name":"Mantes-la-Jolie (Mantes-la-Jolie)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:64199","name":"Plaisir - Grignon (Plaisir)"}}],"disruption_id":"3979f5e6-7785-4eb5